text: Hans Schönenberger (born 30 December 1926) is a Swiss former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Swiss male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Switzerland Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from the canton of St. Gallen
